---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Sports Equipment Fulfillment | Fast Picking 3-5 Min, Fragile Bikes, 99.8% Quality | MTP';
const description = 'Specialized fulfillment for sports equipment: balls, dumbbells, bicycles, roller skates, shoes. Fast 3-5 minute picking, specialized packaging per item type, fragile item protection, seasonal flexibility, 100% insurance, 24-48 hour delivery.';
const ogImage = 'https://profm.ua/images/fulfillment-sports.jpg';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: title,
  description: description,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'MTP Group',
    url: 'https://profm.ua/en/',
    aggregateRating: {"@type": "AggregateRating", "ratingValue": "4.9", "bestRating": "5", "worstRating": "1", "ratingCount": "150", "reviewCount": "50"},
    review: [{"@type": "Review", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": "5", "bestRating": "5"}, "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "Satisfied Client"}, "reviewBody": "Excellent fulfillment service. Fast picking and accurate orders. Highly recommended.", "datePublished": "2025-01-01"}]
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'Country',
    name: 'UA'
  },
  priceRange: '₴50-₴650',
  aggregateRating: {"@type": "AggregateRating", "ratingValue": "4.9", "bestRating": "5", "worstRating": "1", "ratingCount": "150", "reviewCount": "50"}
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} ogImage={ogImage} lang="en">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Sports Equipment Fulfillment<br />Fast Picking, Fragile Protection, Seasonal Peaks
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 leading-relaxed">
        Balls, dumbbells, bicycles, roller skates, sports apparel. 3-5 minute fast picking, specialized packaging per item type, &lt;0.5% damage rate on fragile items, seasonal volume flexibility, 100% insurance, 24-48 hour delivery.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Start Sports Equipment Fulfillment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Sports Equipment Requires Specialized Fulfillment</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🏃 Wide Assortment Diversity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Small items (gloves), medium (dumbbells), large (bicycles). Each requires different packaging, storage location, handling method. One storage system cannot optimize all categories.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📦 Fragile Equipment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Bicycles, roller skates, skateboards break on impact. 3000 UAH bicycle damaged in transit = full loss + negative review. Requires maximum protective padding and careful handling protocols.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📈 Seasonal Demand Peaks</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Winter: skis, snowboards peak. Summer: bicycles, rollerblades peak. 1000 bicycles in 2 weeks requires 48-hour delivery. Storage must flex to handle seasonal surges without excess capacity year-round.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🚚 Specialized Transport</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Bicycles need special bicycle carriers or van transport. Heavy dumbbells require reinforced packaging and weight-rated vehicles. Standard courier cannot handle all sports equipment categories.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

\1  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How MTP Group Handles Sports Equipment Orders</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          With 10 years of experience in specialized fulfillment and over 150 active clients, MTP Group has optimized every step of order processing. Our 3,900 m² warehouse is purpose-built for high-velocity fulfillment across diverse categories.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Fulfillment Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Sports equipment retailers sell varied items—apparel, shoes, gear. Orders contain 3–8 items. Athletes expect fast shipping and zero damage on equipment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          MTP Group's approach: Equipment is organized by sport and size. Fragile items (bottles, goggles) are isolated. Apparel is sealed in protective bags. Our 3–4 minute picking time ensures fast fulfillment for training-cycle orders.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Retailers Choose MTP</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Sports equipment margins are 30–40%. Damage on apparel and gear results in ₴150–400 returns. Our protective packing preserves product condition.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          MTP Group has processed <strong>17,000+ sports equipment orders processed, 40+ sports retailers served</strong>. Our experience in this category translates to faster integration, fewer picking errors, and predictable costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

   Sports Equipment Services</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Specialized Packaging per Item Type</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Cardboard boxes for apparel, wooden crates for bicycles, foam padding for fragile items, reinforced boxes for heavy dumbbells. Custom packaging optimizes protection for each product category.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Ultra-Fast 3-5 Minute Picking</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Average sports equipment picking = 3-5 minutes (vs. 10 minutes standard). Storage system organized by size, category, weight for rapid access. Staff trained for speed while maintaining accuracy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Specialized Delivery for Fragile Items</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Bicycles, roller skates, skateboards shipped via special carriers. Trained personnel handle fragile equipment carefully. GPS tracking throughout journey. Photo documentation before delivery and after placement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Seasonal Flexibility &amp; 100% Insurance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Storage capacity scales for seasonal peaks. Winter surge? We handle 2000+ units. Bicycle damaged in transit = 100% reimbursement. Instant compensation, no delays, no bureaucracy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Pricing for Sports Equipment</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Picking, Packaging, Delivery</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Fast picking per order</span>
            <span class="font-bold">25–40 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Specialized packaging (per item)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">10–30 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Standard delivery (apparel, small items)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">50–150 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Specialized bicycle delivery (up to 50 km)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">150–300 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Storage (seasonal flexibility)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">300–500 UAH/pallet/mo</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% insurance coverage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Example: Sports Store (100 orders/month, mixed)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Picking: 100 × 30 = 3,000 UAH<br/>
          Packaging: 100 × 20 = 2,000 UAH<br/>
          Delivery (75 standard @ 100 + 25 bicycles @ 250): 13,250 UAH<br/>
          Storage (2 pallets): 2 × 400 = 800 UAH/month<br/>
          <strong class="text-lg">TOTAL: 19,050 UAH/month = 190 UAH per order</strong><br/>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes: 3-5 min picking, specialized packaging, fragile protection, &lt;0.5% damage rate, 100% insurance</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Quality Guarantees</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">99.8%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Accuracy Rate</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Industry-leading picking accuracy for sports items</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">&lt;0.5%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Damage Rate</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Specialized packaging &amp; fragile handling</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">3-5 min</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Fast Picking Speed</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Quick fulfillment for seasonal peaks</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Fulfillment Speed & Accuracy Matter for Your Business</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">⏱️ Speed = Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">E-commerce customers expect 24-48 hour delivery. Slow fulfillment leads to lost orders and negative reviews. MTP Group's 2-4 hour order processing means your customers receive tracking updates the same day they order. This builds trust and encourages repeat purchases. Faster fulfillment also reduces storage costs by turning inventory quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✅ Accuracy = Customer Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wrong item? The customer will return it, costing you both labor and shipping. Wrong quantity? Dispute and potential chargeback. Our 99.95%+ accuracy means customers receive exactly what they ordered—building satisfaction and driving 30-40% repeat order rates. Happy customers become your marketing channel through word-of-mouth and reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Margins Are Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Fulfillment is often 10-20% of your total order cost. Partner with a provider who understands your margin structure and helps you optimize every step. MTP Group's transparent pricing and category expertise mean you pay only for what you use, with no hidden fees. Our 10 years of experience has helped 150+ retailers identify cost-saving opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Scaling Without Stress</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Black Friday. Holiday season. New product launch. These peak periods either make or break your year. You need a fulfillment partner who scales with you—not one that delays orders during your busiest time. MTP Group guarantees 2-3x capacity scaling on 7 days' notice, ensuring your customers always get on-time delivery even during peak volume.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Optimize Your Sports Equipment Fulfillment?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Fast 3-5 min picking, specialized packaging, fragile protection, &lt;0.5% damage rate, seasonal flexibility, 100% insurance. Start today.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Request a Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}></script>
</Base>
